    },
    {
      "idx": 1,
      "start": 1192.0,
      "end": 1194.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "像我這種江錯就錯的,想得很開。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 2,
      "start": 1195.4,
      "end": 1199.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我為什麼會這麼說呢?因為大家生活中最上會遇到不快了嘛,對吧?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 3,
      "start": 1199.4,
      "end": 1200.4,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我希望你快樂。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 4,
      "start": 1200.4,
      "end": 1207.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "然後呢,這個因為最近我火了之後,很多人把董宇輝當成了一個關係很好的朋友,向他傾訴內心的這個愁苦。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 5,
      "start": 1207.0,
      "end": 1210.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我其實收到很多的消息,但我真的第一個我看不完,第二個我也回不完。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 6,
      "start": 1211.0,
      "end": 1216.4,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我前兩天拿了手機,大家知道,因為我這個抖音睡一覺起來漲幾十萬粉絲,睡一覺漲四五十萬粉絲。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 7,
      "start": 1216.5,
      "end": 1217.4,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "都在給我發消息。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 8,
      "start": 1217.5,
      "end": 1222.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我的手機折一打開抖音,屏幕就變白了,就發燙,就關機了,就自動關機了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 9,
      "start": 1222.2,
      "end": 1226.3,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我姐姐應該是聽到了,很心疼我,給我寄了一個新的手機過來,還挺感動的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 10,
      "start": 1227.0,
      "end": 1229.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我這兩天收到了好幾個莫名的快遞,挺感動的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 11,
      "start": 1229.2,
      "end": 1231.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "然後我以為是誰給我買這麼貴的東西,我姐說他買的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 12,
      "start": 1232.2,
      "end": 1233.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我現在能打開了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 13,
      "start": 1233.4,
      "end": 1236.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我看了很多朋友跟我講的故事,有的講自己",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 14,
      "start": 1237.0,
      "end": 1240.3,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "生意失敗了,感覺人生失無可失的故事。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 15,
      "start": 1241.0,
      "end": 1246.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "有的講,比如說自己的父親因為生了重病,幾天先離開了他的故事。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 16,
      "start": 1246.2,
      "end": 1248.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "他感覺他的人生",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
