      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 52,
      "start": 1350.2,
      "end": 1351.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "絕望是人性。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 53,
      "start": 1351.4,
      "end": 1352.5,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "但人為什麼在修煉?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 54,
      "start": 1353.1,
      "end": 1357.3,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "人的修煉就是在自己的身上克服人性的缺點,在自己的身上克服這個時代。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 55,
      "start": 1357.5,
      "end": 1361.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "如果你總是第一時間順從自己的內心,那就是認慫。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 56,
      "start": 1361.2,
      "end": 1362.7,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "慫就是尊從自己的心呢。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 57,
      "start": 1363.3,
      "end": 1364.3,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "與自己抗爭。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 58,
      "start": 1364.6,
      "end": 1365.5,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "跟自己修煉。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 59,
      "start": 1365.7,
      "end": 1366.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "說慫人面前全是卡爾。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 60,
      "start": 1367.7,
      "end": 1368.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "他可能現在自己都不記得了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 61,
      "start": 1369.7,
      "end": 1370.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "好多年前我聽他說這句話。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 62,
      "start": 1373.9,
      "end": 1375.7,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "這是新東方轉型的直播間。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 63,
      "start": 1376.0,
      "end": 1376.8,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "東方甄選。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 64,
      "start": 1377.1,
      "end": 1379.6,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我叫董宇輝,我是一個教了八年的高中英語老師。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 65,
      "start": 1379.8,
      "end": 1380.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我今天心情很好。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 66,
      "start": 1381.1,
      "end": 1384.3,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "今天心好的主要原因是因為我今天收到了很多我的學生給我的反饋。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 67,
      "start": 1384.8,
      "end": 1385.7,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "他們很開心。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 68,
      "start": 1386.5,
      "end": 1387.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "他說老師我英語考得很好。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 69,
      "start": 1388.8,
      "end": 1391.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "或者有孩子說老師我考得不怎麼樣好。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 70,
      "start": 1391.9,
      "end": 1392.8,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "但我不糾結了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 71,
      "start": 1393.0,
      "end": 1393.8,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我人生無憾了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 72,
      "start": 1394.0,
      "end": 1394.8,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我高中努力過。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 73,
      "start": 1395.6,
      "end": 1398.4,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我特別害怕他們把勝負看得特別重,我害怕他們把結果看得特別重。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 74,
      "start": 1398.4,
      "end": 1399.5,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "以至於患得患失啊。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 75,
      "start": 1399.5,
      "end": 1402.4,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "所以我其實認識他們幾年,我一直在給他們說結果不重要。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 76,
      "start": 1403.2,
      "end": 1404.4,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "內心無愧才重要。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 77,
      "start": 1405.3,
      "end": 1410.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "就像你中間離開這個城市,離開這個世界,你重要的只是你怎麼樣過好這一生。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 78,
      "start": 1410.0,
      "end": 1412.6,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "有孩子跟我說老師可能我沒有期待中那麼好。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 79,
      "start": 1413.4,
      "end": 1414.5,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "但是我內心無憾了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 80,
      "start": 1414.8,
      "end": 1418.6,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "就像老師經常所說的,得到的是得到的叫青春。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 81,
      "start": 1418.8,
      "end": 1420.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "錯過的叫人生。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 82,
      "start": 1420.9,
      "end": 1422.7,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "不一定總非得得償所願。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 83,
      "start": 1423.0,
      "end": 1424.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "人生有時候的美好就在於陰差陽錯。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 84,
      "start": 1425.6,
      "end": 1428.1,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "陰差陽錯的才能去那些城市,才能見那些人啊。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 85,
      "start": 1428.4,
      "end": 1430.4,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "陰差陽錯的才能展開一段奇旅。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 86,
      "start": 1431.0,
      "end": 1433.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "陰差陽錯的後來你才能去新東方當一個老師。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 87,
      "start": 1434.1,
      "end": 1437.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "陰差陽錯的當了一個老師之後,你才教了50萬的學生。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 88,
      "start": 1437.3,
      "end": 1442.6,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "陰差陽錯的你後來才能站在屏幕前賣菜,給別人露露大臉,能講你的故事。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 89,
      "start": 1443.5,
      "end": 1444.8,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "對不起,我這次講活著吧。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 90,
      "start": 1444.8,
      "end": 1446.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "活著講成了這樣子。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 91,
      "start": 1446.9,
      "end": 1450.6,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "但是,我相信每個人也從我這裡文字裡能夠感受到我想傳遞的力量。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 92,
      "start": 1450.6,
      "end": 1452.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "導演,這樣講有賣出去嗎?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 93,
      "start": 1452.2,
      "end": 1453.6,
      "speaker": "guest",
      "text": "賣出去了,4000多萬。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 94,
      "start": 1453.8,
      "end": 1454.8,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "啊,賣得不好是吧?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 95,
      "start": 1454.8,
      "end": 1455.5,
      "speaker": "guest",
      "text": "還行,挺好。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 96,
      "start": 1456.2,
      "end": 1456.5,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 97,
      "start": 1457.1,
      "end": 1458.3,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "行,還是得寫小作文。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 98,
      "start": 1459.0,
      "end": 1460.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "咱今天晚上賣橄欖油是吧?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 99,
      "start": 1460.5,
      "end": 1461.6,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "西班牙的橄欖油是嗎?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 100,
      "start": 1461.6,
      "end": 1462.0,
      "speaker": "guest",
      "text": "可以。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 101,
      "start": 1462.3,
      "end": 1463.5,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "安達盧西亞那個地方是吧?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 102,
      "start": 1463.8,
      "end": 1464.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "好。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 103,
      "start": 1468.3,
      "end": 1469.3,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "來,把油給我。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 104,
      "start": 1472.0,
      "end": 1476.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "Extra virgin olive oil,特級初榨橄欖油的意思就是",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 105,
      "start": 1476.0,
      "end": 1478.3,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "橄欖果摘下來24小時之內就炸了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 106,
      "start": 1479.4,
      "end": 1480.8,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "鮮,所以口感好。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 107,
      "start": 1481.0,
      "end": 1482.6,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "國外進的油,回來灌裝。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 108,
      "start": 1482.8,
      "end": 1483.8,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "酸度很重要。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 109,
      "start": 1484.1,
      "end": 1485.6,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "好的油,酸度就比較低。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 110,
      "start": 1485.9,
      "end": 1491.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "當然自然炸出來的酸度低,有的人他是通過後期的這個化學手段故意把酸度降低,那不算。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 111,
      "start": 1491.6,
      "end": 1498.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "國標是小於等於0.8%,我們的酸度是小於等於0.6%,口感風味營養得到很大的保存。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 112,
      "start": 1500.6,
      "end": 1501.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "原產國是西班牙。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 113,
      "start": 1503.3,
      "end": 1504.7,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我好多年前去過西班牙。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 114,
      "start": 1505.6,
      "end": 1507.4,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "想到了,我準備寫小作文了啊。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 115,
      "start": 1507.7,
      "end": 1509.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "大家想錄的朋友可以準備好。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 116,
      "start": 1509.2,
      "end": 1510.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "看看現在幾點。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 117,
      "start": 1511.2,
      "end": 1512.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "8點55。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 118,
      "start": 1512.6,
      "end": 1513.8,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我們要不要等個9點?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 119,
      "start": 1517.9,
      "end": 1520.6,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "想到西班牙,我首先想到的是馬德里的藝術館。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 120,
      "start": 1520.9,
      "end": 1522.7,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我在裡頭看到過達利的作品。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 121,
      "start": 1523.6,
      "end": 1526.5,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我想到的是那些穿越的歷史。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 122,
      "start": 1527.5,
      "end": 1529.5,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "仍然停留的宮殿。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 123,
      "start": 1532.0,
      "end": 1536.7,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我想到巴塞羅那,我想到地中海的海岸,想到了",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 124,
      "start": 1537.4,
      "end": 1540.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "灌在杯子裡的三個利亞。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 125,
      "start": 1542.0,
      "end": 1544.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "和端到你面前的海鮮飯。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 126,
      "start": 1547.0,
      "end": 1551.6,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我想到安達盧西亞,他是西班牙最南部,也是歐洲最南部的一個城市。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 127,
      "start": 1552.5,
      "end": 1556.1,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "他與直布羅陀海峽呢,緊鄰著。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 128,
      "start": 1556.4,
      "end": 1559.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "所以直布羅陀海峽將歐洲與非洲切斷。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 1
    },
    {
      "idx": 129,
      "start": 1561.0,
      "end": 1562.4,
